title: Early WR Rankings Part 2 + Deebo Drama, Party Time! - Fantasy Football Podcast for 4/21
description:
The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode, one week before the NFL Draft! On today’s fantasy football podcast, Andy, Mike and Jason continue with their early WR rankings! Which players have the ability to be fantasy draft values? Plus, Deebo Samuel wants to be traded! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for April 21st, 2022.

The 2022 UDK is available for pre-order at UltimateDraftKit.com -- Get instant access to the Dynasty Pass with the UDK+

(07:55) - NFL News (Deebo Samuel)
(22:15) - Wide Receiver Rankings Part 2
(23:30) - CeeDee Lamb
(27:15) - Tee Higgins
(29:45) - Keenan Allen
(32:45) - Jaylen Waddle
(35:35) - DK Metcalf
